name: Cafe La Baguette [Version 1.0]
description:
wow you just moved into a new town called la crescent street and got a job from one of the best cafes in town (wow so cool you even get to date one of them)

you will meet new friends, new foes.. even one or two of them knowing this is a simple game. will you win their heart, or will you not? find out by playing the game.

hey guys note from the developer please note that this game isn't finished yet and will have some updates until its finally complete, thank you and please report bugs in our discord server linked below
